Package tap.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TableIterator
    Let's iterate on each row and then on each column over a table dataset.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LimitedTableIterator
    Wrap a TableIterator in order to limit its reading to a fixed number of rows.
    ResultSetTableIterator
    TableIterator which lets iterate over a SQL ResultSet.
    VOTableIterator
    TableIterator which lets iterate over a VOTable input stream using STIL.
    VOTableIterator.StreamVOTableSink
    This class lets consume the metadata and rows of a VOTable document.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataReadException
    Exception that occurs when reading a data input (can be an InputStream, a ResultSet, a SavotTable, ...).
